Grammar

    0 $accept: prog $end

    1 prog: lines

    2 lines: ε
    3      | line NEWLINE lines

    4 line: exprs

    5 exprs: ε
    6      | expr
    7      | expr SPACE exprs

    8 expr: CMD arith_expr
    9     | assignment
   10     | SPECIAL_CMD
   11     | CUSTOM_VAR SPACE INT
   12     | CUSTOM_VAR SPACE FLOAT
   13     | COMMENT

   14 assignment: VAR SET arith_expr
